This is the monorepo for @three-use, an three.js utility library.

The monorepo uses pnpm, and is organized using workspaces.

The workspaces are:

- packages/core: Core utilities for three.js.
- playground: playground for the library.

This project is written in typescript.

If you want to check types, you can run `pnpm check` from the root of the repo. 

If you want add interface or type, please add inline comments. such as, /** description of the type */.

If you want add comments, please use English.

If you want add codes, please use functional programming style., don't use class.
